1
00:00:10,970 --> 00:00:12,896
(South City
Chinese and Western Medicine Clinic)

2
00:00:18,550 --> 00:00:19,480
Got a lighter?

3
00:00:31,700 --> 00:00:33,700
=Cases Between Us=

4
00:00:33,700 --> 00:00:36,260
(Ge Fan, Attending Physician,
South City Medicine Clinic)

5
00:00:36,260 --> 00:00:38,900
=Episode 25=

6
00:00:58,688 --> 00:01:00,608
(Ge Fan, General Practitioner,
South City Medicine Clinic)

7
00:01:00,790 --> 00:01:01,750
Ge Fan?

8
00:01:02,320 --> 00:01:03,470
You're a woman?

9
00:01:04,040 --> 00:01:05,200
And you're not blind?

10
00:01:05,200 --> 00:01:05,790
No.

11
00:01:05,790 --> 00:01:07,070
No, that's not what I meant.

12
00:01:07,950 --> 00:01:08,710
I'm Du Wenjiu.

13
00:01:08,800 --> 00:01:10,464
I just spoke
with Dr. Cheng on the phone.

14
00:01:10,512 --> 00:01:11,480
He asked me to pick up

15
00:01:11,480 --> 00:01:12,510
Zhang Dalu's records.

16
00:01:12,840 --> 00:01:14,590
He said you were his second-in-command.

17
00:01:16,150 --> 00:01:17,040
I didn't expect

18
00:01:21,840 --> 00:01:22,840
you to be this beautiful.

19
00:01:26,000 --> 00:01:26,920
No, not beautiful.

20
00:01:28,280 --> 00:01:28,790
No.

21
00:01:29,120 --> 00:01:30,208
No, that's not.

22
00:01:43,280 --> 00:01:44,790
You know Dr. Cheng?

23
00:01:45,632 --> 00:01:47,710
I was lucky enough
to have dinner with him once.

24
00:01:47,710 --> 00:01:49,070
He's close with our department head.

25
00:01:49,340 --> 00:01:50,280
(File)

26
00:01:50,280 --> 00:01:51,310
You're from Peking Union?

27
00:01:51,710 --> 00:01:52,120
Yes.

28
00:01:52,192 --> 00:01:53,392
Cardiothoracic Surgery.

29
00:01:57,230 --> 00:01:58,950
The patient arrived here

30
00:01:58,950 --> 00:02:00,150
at 6:19 PM yesterday.

31
00:02:00,510 --> 00:02:02,070
I gave him a cardiac stimulant,

32
00:02:02,590 --> 00:02:04,150
but we couldn't save him.

33
00:02:05,950 --> 00:02:07,280
He was pronounced dead at 6:40 PM.

34
00:02:07,488 --> 00:02:09,264
His body was taken away at 7:30 PM?

35
00:02:09,520 --> 00:02:11,470
By the corpse carriers
called by the Zhang troupe.

36
00:02:12,300 --> 00:02:14,100
(Death Certificate)

37
00:02:14,150 --> 00:02:15,840
Bleeding from the mouth and nose.

38
00:02:15,840 --> 00:02:17,190
Conjunctival congestion.

39
00:02:23,800 --> 00:02:25,520
Dark purplish lividity.

40
00:02:26,400 --> 00:02:28,680
Shouldn't the cause of death be
cardiac arrest

41
00:02:28,680 --> 00:02:30,590
from the blow to the chest?

42
00:02:31,750 --> 00:02:33,840
That was my assessment,

43
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:35,240
based on the witnesses' statements

44
00:02:35,240 --> 00:02:36,840
and the body's condition.

45
00:02:38,870 --> 00:02:40,150
Why didn't Dr. Cheng sign it?

46
00:02:40,910 --> 00:02:42,000
Didn't he tell you?

47
00:02:42,720 --> 00:02:44,220
He's away providing free medical care.

48
00:02:44,710 --> 00:02:46,190
I'm in charge

49
00:02:46,520 --> 00:02:47,750
of the clinic for now.

50
00:02:48,840 --> 00:02:50,150
If he'd been here...

51
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:55,280
he could've saved him.

52
00:02:57,150 --> 00:02:58,400
Don't blame yourself.

53
00:02:58,400 --> 00:02:59,664
You did everything you could.

54
00:03:05,030 --> 00:03:06,680
You help the police, too?

55
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:10,190
Are doctors at Peking Union
short of money?

56
00:03:12,310 --> 00:03:13,360
It's not about the money.

57
00:03:14,190 --> 00:03:14,800
Uh...

58
00:03:16,310 --> 00:03:17,560
It's a hobby.

59
00:03:19,360 --> 00:03:20,150
I do it for fun.

60
00:03:20,750 --> 00:03:23,030
Once I examine the body tonight,

61
00:03:23,030 --> 00:03:24,400
I'll catch the killer in no time.

62
00:03:24,710 --> 00:03:25,960
You're that good?

63
00:03:25,960 --> 00:03:26,590
Of course.

64
00:03:26,840 --> 00:03:28,560
Solving cases takes brains,

65
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:29,984
and that's one thing I don't lack.

66
00:03:32,310 --> 00:03:32,910
Goodbye.

67
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:38,680
Miss Ge.

68
00:03:42,560 --> 00:03:43,800
Are you free tonight?

69
00:03:47,400 --> 00:03:48,960
I mean, if you are,

70
00:03:48,960 --> 00:03:50,750
you could come with me. We could

71
00:03:51,648 --> 00:03:52,870
examine a body or something.

72
00:03:55,310 --> 00:03:56,750
Are you asking me on a date?

73
00:03:57,870 --> 00:03:59,030
No.

74
00:03:59,030 --> 00:04:01,376
Asking a girl out like that
would be too forward, especially

75
00:04:02,560 --> 00:04:03,920
with a dead body involved.

76
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:04,840
And?

77
00:04:06,680 --> 00:04:07,190
Fine.

78
00:04:12,840 --> 00:04:14,000
Fine?

79
00:04:15,840 --> 00:04:17,750
What does that mean?

80
00:04:52,160 --> 00:04:52,680
Eat.

81
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:55,750
You can eat,

82
00:04:56,190 --> 00:04:57,070
but promise me.

83
00:04:57,070 --> 00:04:58,120
After you finish eating,

84
00:04:58,560 --> 00:05:00,120
you have to tell me

85
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:01,560
everything you know.

86
00:05:03,430 --> 00:05:05,190
I knew I couldn't fool you.

87
00:05:07,070 --> 00:05:08,040
Don't forget

88
00:05:08,310 --> 00:05:10,070
what you told me

89
00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:11,430
the first time we met.

90
00:05:11,860 --> 00:05:14,100
(Safe Journey, Mourning)

91
00:05:28,510 --> 00:05:29,870
What's wrong with you?

92
00:05:30,510 --> 00:05:32,120
Are you blind?

93
00:05:32,400 --> 00:05:34,480
(Mourning)
You're stealing offerings for the dead?

94
00:05:36,160 --> 00:05:37,270
I don't believe in those.

95
00:05:37,830 --> 00:05:39,070
If ghosts were real,

96
00:05:39,070 --> 00:05:41,120
my mother's ghost
would've looked after me.

97
00:05:41,120 --> 00:05:42,270
I wouldn't be going hungry.

98
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:44,160
Once you're dead, that's the end.

99
00:05:44,720 --> 00:05:46,160
If I don't eat it, it'll go to waste.

100
00:05:46,390 --> 00:05:48,430
They'll be making offerings here
for forty-nine days.

101
00:05:48,832 --> 00:05:49,830
You can always come back.

102
00:05:52,750 --> 00:05:53,800
That's my eldest uncle.

103
00:05:53,800 --> 00:05:56,040
You don't believe in ghosts,

104
00:05:56,080 --> 00:05:57,630
yet early this morning,
you were shouting

105
00:05:57,664 --> 00:05:59,420
that Zhang Dalu had come back
from the dead.

106
00:05:59,488 --> 00:06:00,600
The whole South City

107
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:02,190
is now talking about it.

108
00:06:02,390 --> 00:06:04,510
I thought you were
helping Zhang Dalu slip away

109
00:06:04,510 --> 00:06:06,190
from Hu Mingwu.

110
00:06:06,480 --> 00:06:08,040
But Zhang Dalu really is dead.

111
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:11,270
What are you up to?

112
00:06:12,270 --> 00:06:15,720
I wanted to see
how Hu Mingwu would react.

113
00:06:16,360 --> 00:06:18,070
You think Hu Mingwu

114
00:06:18,070 --> 00:06:19,240
killed Zhang Dalu?

115
00:06:19,480 --> 00:06:21,360
He's the only one who wanted Dalu dead.

116
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:23,070
After Dalu beat him up
a few days ago,

117
00:06:23,070 --> 00:06:24,360
he went into hiding.

118
00:06:24,360 --> 00:06:25,680
So he sent people to Tianjin

119
00:06:25,680 --> 00:06:26,720
to bring his parents here

120
00:06:26,720 --> 00:06:28,040
as hostages,

121
00:06:28,600 --> 00:06:29,920
forcing him to apologize.

122
00:06:30,370 --> 00:06:31,560
Knowing Master Hu,

123
00:06:31,560 --> 00:06:33,000
he would've chopped off his hand.

124
00:06:33,480 --> 00:06:35,270
A few days ago, I overheard

125
00:06:35,410 --> 00:06:36,140
Dalu and Cong

126
00:06:36,160 --> 00:06:38,040
discussing how to get out of it.

127
00:06:39,680 --> 00:06:40,430
By faking his death?

128
00:06:42,630 --> 00:06:43,630
How did you know?

129
00:06:46,950 --> 00:06:48,000
Dr. Du got this report

130
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:49,830
from the clinic.

131
00:06:49,830 --> 00:06:51,190
It lists the cause of death

132
00:06:51,560 --> 00:06:52,830
as cardiac arrest.

133
00:06:53,430 --> 00:06:55,750
I was there the day
he performed the chest-breaking act.

134
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:57,630
The stone was rectangular,

135
00:06:57,870 --> 00:07:00,190
with a contact area about this wide.

136
00:07:00,360 --> 00:07:01,800
From a physics standpoint,

137
00:07:01,872 --> 00:07:04,310
the hammer's force is concentrated
on one point of the stone,

138
00:07:04,310 --> 00:07:05,216
so the stone shatters.

139
00:07:05,220 --> 00:07:07,300
But once that force
is applied to a person's chest,

140
00:07:07,312 --> 00:07:07,870
it spreads out.

141
00:07:07,870 --> 00:07:09,360
Every traveling troupe

142
00:07:09,360 --> 00:07:10,800
does this act.

143
00:07:10,830 --> 00:07:12,630
Even if the blow were a bit too hard,

144
00:07:12,870 --> 00:07:14,390
it should've injured his lungs,

145
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:15,830
not his heart.

146
00:07:16,070 --> 00:07:16,830
That means

147
00:07:18,256 --> 00:07:19,630
the doctor who wrote this report

148
00:07:19,630 --> 00:07:21,120
was in on it with Zhang Dalu.

149
00:07:25,480 --> 00:07:26,160
Douding,

150
00:07:27,072 --> 00:07:28,750
was faking his death
as part of his plan?

151
00:07:29,270 --> 00:07:30,390
I'm not sure.

152
00:07:31,240 --> 00:07:32,070
But...

153
00:07:36,830 --> 00:07:38,390
that hand signal was our code.

154
00:07:39,140 --> 00:07:40,140
(Ironman Zhang)

155
00:07:40,430 --> 00:07:41,430
I can't do it anymore.

156
00:07:49,830 --> 00:07:50,510
Girl,

157
00:07:50,800 --> 00:07:51,950
if you see me do this

158
00:07:51,950 --> 00:07:53,360
during a performance...

159
00:07:57,160 --> 00:07:59,270
It means I can't take any more.

160
00:07:59,270 --> 00:08:01,190
No matter how much the crowd eggs us on,

161
00:08:01,190 --> 00:08:02,750
don't let them add another stone.

162
00:08:02,750 --> 00:08:03,430
Got it?

163
00:08:05,190 --> 00:08:06,830
That was our signal.

164
00:08:07,240 --> 00:08:09,480
So when Dalu came looking for me
at a cheap Inn,

165
00:08:09,480 --> 00:08:10,600
he was asking for help.

166
00:08:10,950 --> 00:08:11,680
Then?

167
00:08:12,040 --> 00:08:13,120
I ran outside,

168
00:08:13,750 --> 00:08:14,830
and he was gone.

169
00:08:17,720 --> 00:08:18,600
Dalu!

170
00:08:19,000 --> 00:08:20,190
Dalu!

171
00:08:21,310 --> 00:08:22,480
Then I went to the house

172
00:08:22,480 --> 00:08:24,310
he'd asked me to rent.

173
00:08:24,310 --> 00:08:25,830
It's near the inn.

174
00:08:26,160 --> 00:08:28,800
He said no one could know

175
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:30,240
about the place.

176
00:08:30,680 --> 00:08:32,150
So after faking his death,

177
00:08:32,150 --> 00:08:33,390
he planned to hide there?

178
00:08:34,390 --> 00:08:35,240
Probably.

179
00:08:36,510 --> 00:08:37,870
I didn't find him.

180
00:08:38,870 --> 00:08:41,100
But I found this outside the door.

181
00:08:41,100 --> 00:08:42,380
(Zhang)

182
00:08:44,440 --> 00:08:45,440
Strength Pills.

183
00:08:48,670 --> 00:08:50,480
(Zhang)
The Zhang troupe's secret remedy.

184
00:08:50,480 --> 00:08:51,910
Dalu took them every day

185
00:08:51,910 --> 00:08:52,840
to build muscle.

186
00:08:53,030 --> 00:08:54,390
Do you think they worked?

187
00:08:54,390 --> 00:08:56,360
Judging by his build, I'd say they did.

188
00:08:56,360 --> 00:08:58,320
But besides those,

189
00:08:58,320 --> 00:09:00,200
he also ate three or four eggs

190
00:09:00,200 --> 00:09:01,360
and a huge drumstick,

191
00:09:01,360 --> 00:09:02,750
and carried dried meat with him.

192
00:09:02,800 --> 00:09:04,576
Whenever he got hungry, he'd eat some.

193
00:09:04,910 --> 00:09:05,870
Do you still have any?

194
00:09:06,200 --> 00:09:07,480
I've got two left.

195
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:08,670
Oh, right.

196
00:09:08,670 --> 00:09:10,600
The last time I scraped my leg,

197
00:09:10,600 --> 00:09:12,752
Dalu crushed half a pill
and put it on the wound.

198
00:09:12,976 --> 00:09:14,560
The pain disappeared instantly.

199
00:09:16,080 --> 00:09:17,390
Besides the pain going away,

200
00:09:17,390 --> 00:09:18,550
did you feel anything else?

201
00:09:19,240 --> 00:09:20,000
Anything else?

202
00:09:20,670 --> 00:09:21,510
No.

203
00:09:21,790 --> 00:09:22,240
Dalu

204
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:23,840
always carried those pills with him.

205
00:09:23,840 --> 00:09:25,150
So he must've been there.

206
00:09:25,584 --> 00:09:28,150
Someone must've discovered
he was planning to fake his death,

207
00:09:28,150 --> 00:09:30,000
tracked him down, and killed him.

208
00:09:30,790 --> 00:09:32,440
I thought it was Master Hu.

209
00:09:41,630 --> 00:09:43,056
But judging by Hu Mingwu's reaction,

210
00:09:43,088 --> 00:09:44,440
before the coffin was opened,

211
00:09:44,440 --> 00:09:46,550
he wasn't sure Zhang Dalu
had faked his death.

212
00:09:48,480 --> 00:09:49,510
Then who

213
00:09:50,670 --> 00:09:52,270
could've secretly
moved Zhang Dalu's body

214
00:09:52,270 --> 00:09:55,030
back to the Zhang troupe?

215
00:09:56,390 --> 00:09:57,550
Someone from the troupe.

216
00:09:58,270 --> 00:09:59,120
Smart guess.

217
00:10:00,030 --> 00:10:00,630
Douding.

218
00:10:01,670 --> 00:10:02,510
Besides Zhang Cong,

219
00:10:02,510 --> 00:10:04,480
who else knew the plan?

220
00:10:04,870 --> 00:10:05,840
No one else.

221
00:10:06,510 --> 00:10:08,000
Were the two close?

222
00:10:08,320 --> 00:10:09,120
Very.

223
00:10:11,510 --> 00:10:12,750
How's Du Wenjiu doing?

224
00:10:14,144 --> 00:10:16,030
Overall, there are
no obvious external injuries

225
00:10:16,030 --> 00:10:17,550
on Zhang Dalu's body.

226
00:10:17,550 --> 00:10:18,600
So I collected samples

227
00:10:18,600 --> 00:10:20,120
of his stomach contents and liver tissue

228
00:10:20,120 --> 00:10:21,080
for toxicology testing.

229
00:10:21,720 --> 00:10:23,960
A few minutes
after the mouse stopped breathing,

230
00:10:23,960 --> 00:10:25,240
its heart stopped, too.

231
00:10:25,240 --> 00:10:26,768
- Tetrodotoxin.
- Tetrodotoxin?

232
00:10:28,120 --> 00:10:30,200
You know

233
00:10:30,200 --> 00:10:31,240
pathology too?

234
00:10:31,440 --> 00:10:33,480
So only you're allowed
to study medicine in Britain?

235
00:10:33,480 --> 00:10:35,504
Can't I want pufferfish
and still be afraid of dying?

236
00:10:35,552 --> 00:10:38,200
I spent a fortune
on a foreign medical book.

237
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:39,030
It says

238
00:10:39,030 --> 00:10:41,088
tetrodotoxin can stop
the heartbeat and breathing,

239
00:10:41,136 --> 00:10:42,848
leave no pulse,
and cause dilated pupils.

240
00:10:42,880 --> 00:10:44,900
The victim looks almost no different
from a corpse.

241
00:10:44,910 --> 00:10:46,240
But with prompt treatment,

242
00:10:46,336 --> 00:10:47,408
they can still be saved.

243
00:10:48,440 --> 00:10:50,200
Looks like being a foodie
does come in handy.

244
00:10:51,120 --> 00:10:53,670
Besides pufferfish poisoning,
did Zhang Dalu show any other signs?

245
00:10:53,670 --> 00:10:54,600
So far,

246
00:10:55,000 --> 00:10:56,270
that's the only cause of death.

247
00:10:56,510 --> 00:10:57,790
Which means

248
00:10:58,750 --> 00:11:00,390
either he intended to fake his death

249
00:11:00,550 --> 00:11:01,960
but accidentally took too much,

250
00:11:02,240 --> 00:11:04,510
or he never intended to take that much,

251
00:11:04,510 --> 00:11:06,030
and someone increased the dose.

252
00:11:06,240 --> 00:11:08,360
There can't be many restaurants
in the capital

253
00:11:08,360 --> 00:11:09,360
serving pufferfish.

254
00:11:10,870 --> 00:11:11,600
Our old friend.

255
00:11:12,670 --> 00:11:13,630
Jingshi No. 1.

256
00:11:13,900 --> 00:11:16,900
(Jingshi No. 1)

257
00:11:16,910 --> 00:11:18,200
After Madam Zhang's arrest,

258
00:11:18,200 --> 00:11:19,960
Mei Fen became the real owner

259
00:11:19,960 --> 00:11:21,320
of Jingshi No. 1.

260
00:11:21,320 --> 00:11:22,550
Even better.

261
00:11:22,550 --> 00:11:24,400
It's always easier with people we know.

262
00:11:26,390 --> 00:11:26,960
Chief Yuan.

263
00:11:26,960 --> 00:11:27,750
Consultant Zhao.

264
00:11:28,270 --> 00:11:29,910
If it's your case, it's my case.

265
00:11:29,910 --> 00:11:31,670
I'll get to the bottom of it today.

266
00:11:31,670 --> 00:11:33,000
To avoid accidents,

267
00:11:33,000 --> 00:11:34,630
we always sealed the pufferfish innards

268
00:11:34,630 --> 00:11:35,910
in separate bags

269
00:11:35,910 --> 00:11:37,776
before sending them away
with the garbage.

270
00:11:39,910 --> 00:11:40,550
Zhang.

271
00:11:41,000 --> 00:11:41,630
Coming.

272
00:11:43,360 --> 00:11:44,120
Ma'am.

273
00:11:45,000 --> 00:11:46,910
You'd better step aside.

274
00:11:48,910 --> 00:11:49,510
Sure thing.

275
00:11:52,304 --> 00:11:53,472
Can I ask you something?

276
00:11:53,632 --> 00:11:54,750
Have you seen this man?

277
00:11:56,840 --> 00:11:57,200
No.

278
00:11:57,200 --> 00:11:57,910
Never seen him.

279
00:11:59,440 --> 00:12:00,030
What about him?

280
00:12:05,270 --> 00:12:06,480
I've seen him.

281
00:12:06,480 --> 00:12:08,200
He came to me privately a few days ago.

282
00:12:08,200 --> 00:12:10,064
He wanted to buy
some frozen pufferfish liver.

283
00:12:10,840 --> 00:12:11,510
Thanks.

284
00:12:11,870 --> 00:12:12,550
No problem.

285
00:12:17,480 --> 00:12:18,120
Chief.

286
00:12:19,200 --> 00:12:20,080
She's looking for you.

287
00:12:21,750 --> 00:12:23,120
Someone went into the house

288
00:12:23,120 --> 00:12:23,910
Dalu rented.

289
00:13:08,540 --> 00:13:09,940
(Gao Yingying)

290
00:13:10,120 --> 00:13:11,200
Eighth Madam Hu?

291
00:13:17,440 --> 00:13:18,720
I summoned you today,

292
00:13:18,720 --> 00:13:20,000
but Hu Mingwu said you'd run away.

293
00:13:20,510 --> 00:13:21,910
I was beaten unconscious

294
00:13:21,910 --> 00:13:23,870
at that time.

295
00:13:24,120 --> 00:13:25,870
He didn't dare let the police see me.

296
00:13:26,320 --> 00:13:28,550
I barely escaped.

297
00:13:29,670 --> 00:13:30,720
It was me.

298
00:13:31,840 --> 00:13:33,790
I got Dalu killed.

299
00:13:34,910 --> 00:13:37,270
At least let me
burn some paper money for him.

300
00:13:38,720 --> 00:13:40,000
You got him killed?

301
00:13:54,960 --> 00:13:56,000
Excuse me.

302
00:13:56,480 --> 00:13:57,600
I'd like to try this on.

303
00:13:57,600 --> 00:13:58,080
Certainly.

304
00:13:58,080 --> 00:13:59,200
This way, please.

305
00:14:02,320 --> 00:14:03,600
Eighth Madam.

306
00:14:05,200 --> 00:14:06,720
I'm going to change.

307
00:14:06,720 --> 00:14:08,144
Are you planning to watch?

308
00:14:21,270 --> 00:14:21,790
Yingying.

309
00:14:32,200 --> 00:14:33,480
Tomorrow afternoon,

310
00:14:33,870 --> 00:14:36,240
Cong and I are going to fake my death.

311
00:14:38,790 --> 00:14:40,200
As long as we fool Hu Mingwu

312
00:14:40,200 --> 00:14:41,270
and he releases my parents,

313
00:14:41,270 --> 00:14:42,510
you leave immediately.

314
00:14:42,720 --> 00:14:43,870
Meet me at this address.

315
00:14:43,960 --> 00:14:45,000
I'll take you away with me.

316
00:14:45,270 --> 00:14:47,390
How are you going to fool him?

317
00:14:47,390 --> 00:14:49,120
Cong got a fake-death drug.

318
00:14:49,550 --> 00:14:50,270
Also,

319
00:14:50,464 --> 00:14:52,630
he's acquainted with the female doctor
at the clinic.

320
00:14:53,200 --> 00:14:54,270
She'll help me.

321
00:14:55,480 --> 00:14:56,320
Really?

322
00:14:56,600 --> 00:14:57,270
Really.

323
00:15:07,200 --> 00:15:08,960
Fake death?

324
00:15:09,870 --> 00:15:12,320
How could that possibly
fool that old fox?

325
00:15:14,928 --> 00:15:16,464
Did Zhang Dalu say anything else

326
00:15:17,150 --> 00:15:18,320
about the fake-death drug?

327
00:15:21,670 --> 00:15:22,630
He said

328
00:15:23,910 --> 00:15:25,200
he tested it.

329
00:15:26,670 --> 00:15:28,200
I'm not an idiot.

330
00:15:28,510 --> 00:15:30,270
I don't believe whatever people tell me.

331
00:15:30,270 --> 00:15:31,480
I tried it

332
00:15:31,480 --> 00:15:32,440
on rabbits

333
00:15:32,440 --> 00:15:33,750
and puppies.

334
00:15:33,960 --> 00:15:35,000
The dose

335
00:15:35,000 --> 00:15:35,870
was tiny.

336
00:15:36,440 --> 00:15:37,480
It couldn't kill them.

337
00:15:37,960 --> 00:15:39,670
My lips would just turn purple,

338
00:15:39,712 --> 00:15:40,750
my pulse would disappear,

339
00:15:41,104 --> 00:15:42,992
but after pouring in
a couple of bowls of liquor,

340
00:15:43,024 --> 00:15:44,960
I'd throw it all up
and be completely fine.

341
00:15:46,630 --> 00:15:47,720
Are you sure?

342
00:15:50,030 --> 00:15:50,840
I am.

343
00:15:52,550 --> 00:15:54,550
If that dose
couldn't even kill an animal,

344
00:15:55,360 --> 00:15:57,390
how could anything have gone wrong?

345
00:15:59,600 --> 00:16:01,480
If only I'd stopped him,

346
00:16:01,480 --> 00:16:02,720
(Zhang)
he wouldn't have died.

347
00:16:03,550 --> 00:16:05,440
This is all my fault.

348
00:16:07,648 --> 00:16:09,150
(Zhang)
No wonder Du Wenjiu said

349
00:16:09,150 --> 00:16:10,790
his stomach was full of Strength Pills.

350
00:16:11,120 --> 00:16:12,600
How many did he take?

351
00:16:14,510 --> 00:16:16,630
You and Zhang Dalu
were from the same village?

352
00:16:17,120 --> 00:16:18,510
When we were kids.

353
00:16:18,960 --> 00:16:19,750
Later,

354
00:16:19,960 --> 00:16:22,270
his parents moved into the city

355
00:16:22,440 --> 00:16:23,550
to make a living.

356
00:16:24,150 --> 00:16:25,000
Do you know

357
00:16:25,000 --> 00:16:26,200
where they lived in Tianjin?

358
00:16:27,870 --> 00:16:29,120
I never asked.

359
00:16:34,080 --> 00:16:35,320
Even you don't know.

360
00:16:36,670 --> 00:16:38,270
Then how did Hu Mingwu's men

361
00:16:38,790 --> 00:16:40,840
find his parents and bring them here?

362
00:16:45,510 --> 00:16:47,510
Someone in the Zhang troupe
must've betrayed him.

363
00:16:49,200 --> 00:16:49,910
Zhang?

364
00:16:55,120 --> 00:16:55,960
What do you think?

365
00:16:58,000 --> 00:16:59,440
Probably the same as you.

366
00:17:00,320 --> 00:17:01,200
Tell me.

367
00:17:01,910 --> 00:17:02,910
Zhang Cong

368
00:17:02,910 --> 00:17:05,110
was probably bought off
by Hu Mingwu long ago.

369
00:17:05,110 --> 00:17:06,030
He deliberately lured

370
00:17:06,030 --> 00:17:07,000
Zhang Dalu into a trap,

371
00:17:07,350 --> 00:17:10,240
claiming he'd help him fake his death,

372
00:17:10,240 --> 00:17:12,440
but he secretly tampered

373
00:17:12,440 --> 00:17:14,200
with the dosage,

374
00:17:14,640 --> 00:17:16,640
turning fake death into a real one.

375
00:17:18,070 --> 00:17:19,830
Now there's only
one missing piece.

376
00:17:20,110 --> 00:17:21,110
The female doctor.

377
00:17:26,550 --> 00:17:27,720
Why did you help Zhang Dalu

378
00:17:27,720 --> 00:17:29,000
forge the death certificate?

379
00:17:30,310 --> 00:17:32,400
Everything I wrote was true.

380
00:17:32,640 --> 00:17:33,510
Did you extract

381
00:17:33,510 --> 00:17:34,920
the tetrodotoxin for him, too?

382
00:17:35,680 --> 00:17:36,640
They came to me.

383
00:17:37,270 --> 00:17:38,550
I didn't extract it.

384
00:17:41,920 --> 00:17:43,400
The process is too dangerous.

385
00:17:44,880 --> 00:17:45,510
Well,

386
00:17:45,830 --> 00:17:47,310
I'll tell you the dosage

387
00:17:47,310 --> 00:17:49,240
and how to extract tetrodotoxin.

388
00:17:49,240 --> 00:17:50,720
But you'll have to carry out

389
00:17:50,720 --> 00:17:52,350
every step yourselves.

390
00:17:52,350 --> 00:17:52,790
But...

391
00:17:52,790 --> 00:17:53,830
I don't know how.

392
00:17:54,680 --> 00:17:55,270
It's fine.

393
00:17:55,270 --> 00:17:56,310
Dr. Ge taught me.

394
00:17:56,310 --> 00:17:57,232
It's not difficult.

395
00:17:58,310 --> 00:17:58,960
Fine.

396
00:18:00,070 --> 00:18:01,270
Knowing the risks,

397
00:18:01,590 --> 00:18:02,830
why did you help him?

398
00:18:07,110 --> 00:18:08,000
Fifty silver coins.

399
00:18:10,720 --> 00:18:12,030
You'd risk all this

400
00:18:13,160 --> 00:18:14,480
for fifty silver coins?

401
00:18:16,000 --> 00:18:18,070
Dr. Cheng is kindhearted.

402
00:18:18,880 --> 00:18:20,310
He charges very little.

403
00:18:20,310 --> 00:18:22,480
He even lets poor patients pay later.

404
00:18:22,784 --> 00:18:24,032
The clinic barely stays afloat,

405
00:18:24,400 --> 00:18:25,830
and we doctors

406
00:18:26,830 --> 00:18:28,070
are barely getting by.

407
00:18:30,160 --> 00:18:31,510
Your excuse...

408
00:18:31,510 --> 00:18:33,590
A doctor's duty is to save lives.

409
00:18:33,880 --> 00:18:35,440
By issuing a false death certificate,

410
00:18:35,440 --> 00:18:36,480
I could help Zhang Dalu

411
00:18:36,480 --> 00:18:37,590
escape Hu Mingwu's revenge.

412
00:18:38,160 --> 00:18:39,310
Wasn't I saving him, too?

413
00:18:39,960 --> 00:18:40,720
Tetrodotoxin

414
00:18:40,720 --> 00:18:42,440
usually takes effect
within thirty minutes.

415
00:18:42,960 --> 00:18:43,750
So

416
00:18:43,750 --> 00:18:44,830
you must take it

417
00:18:44,830 --> 00:18:45,750
before the final act

418
00:18:45,750 --> 00:18:46,880
starts.

419
00:18:47,440 --> 00:18:48,640
You'll also need a blood pouch

420
00:18:48,640 --> 00:18:49,720
and face powder.

421
00:18:50,400 --> 00:18:51,640
I've prepared all of that.

422
00:18:51,640 --> 00:18:53,240
Once your breathing and pulse

423
00:18:53,240 --> 00:18:55,160
become extremely weak,

424
00:18:55,160 --> 00:18:56,510
I'll pronounce you dead

425
00:18:56,510 --> 00:18:58,440
and send you to the morgue.

426
00:18:58,440 --> 00:19:00,110
That one-eyed man

427
00:19:00,110 --> 00:19:01,310
will definitely come to check.

428
00:19:01,310 --> 00:19:03,350
He's every bit as suspicious
as Hu Mingwu.

429
00:19:03,350 --> 00:19:04,750
As long as we fool them,

430
00:19:04,750 --> 00:19:06,640
I'll induce vomiting
and revive you immediately.

431
00:19:07,790 --> 00:19:08,440
Don't worry.

432
00:19:08,680 --> 00:19:09,440
It'll be fine.

433
00:19:09,680 --> 00:19:10,310
Alright.

434
00:19:11,110 --> 00:19:11,830
However,

435
00:19:12,288 --> 00:19:13,880
when I was about to induce vomiting,

436
00:19:15,536 --> 00:19:16,860
Zhang Cong changed his mind.

437
00:19:17,100 --> 00:19:19,420
(End of Episode 25)

438
00:19:20,441 --> 00:19:22,081
♪Side by side,
we journey through this life♪

439
00:19:22,081 --> 00:19:23,621
♪Troubled times
are but a laughing matter♪

440
00:19:23,621 --> 00:19:24,871
♪However, the world changes♪

441
00:19:24,871 --> 00:19:26,791
♪You'll still be by my side♪

442
00:19:26,791 --> 00:19:28,481
♪Side by side,
we journey through this life♪

443
00:19:28,481 --> 00:19:30,051
♪Praise and blame come and go♪

444
00:19:30,051 --> 00:19:31,621
♪If this is my final chapter♪

445
00:19:31,621 --> 00:19:34,121
♪I'll solve this mystery with you♪
